{"tid":1931354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒利亞：賽季未完紅軍不可稱王","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:36:57.000Z","uid":72497,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de2b5b21ade18b55520b04286d9020a84d510c23","tid":1931354,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"英格蘭一代中鋒舒利亞認為，英超球季一日未完，利物浦都不該提早封王。<br />\n<br />\n「如果，只是如果，球季無法完成的話，你可能產生贏家或輸家。」前英超神射手舒利亞（Alan Shearer）在專欄寫道。英超暫停之前，利物浦獨佔鰲頭，榜首優勢達到25分，但目前情況來看，球季至少要暫停要4月3日。 「當然，這情況很可怕，對利物浦亦然，但這是唯一的結果。」49歲的舒利亞退役14年，曾短暫任教紐卡素，近年主要靠講波維生，「同樣地，賽程未踢完，就不應該有降班隊或冠軍隊。我明白，這樣說對紅軍實在太殘忍，但比賽就要公平。」 <br />\n<br />\n紅軍上一次贏得頂級聯賽已是1990年，當年英超尚未成立，全球利迷正期待首座英超冠軍，豈料因新冠病毒節外生枝。"},{"pid":"0411b4becce6392e686405a08f8aa379d416e89f","tid":1931354,"uid":7699,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"舒利亞死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d8e3961166f555401a19a8a5ac440c69c497f","tid":1931354,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0411b4becce6392e686405a08f8aa379d416e89f","tid":1931354,"uid":7699,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"舒利亞死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dff4b01dff49f8e41b594414fb89d98ba3aa3f8","tid":1931354,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"近年主要靠講波維生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0885cd9176dcca11a3ef88ac7224090040770f25","tid":1931354,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"d21cd326bacbc6864c421d0c548c1a2ad6a9320c","tid":1931354,"uid":296445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0dff4b01dff49f8e41b594414fb89d